<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Big League Slugger Baseball is a cartoonish, big-head-anime-style baseball game. It uses the standard behind-the-catcher viewpoint for batting and pitching and switches to different views when the ball is hit.
			      <br><br>One or two players can play a single exhibition game, or a single player can play a 10 or 30-game season, which can be saved to a memory card. After completing the season you can proceed to the Final Series.
			      <br><br>The game is unlicensed and does not include any real teams, players, or stadiums, though you can create your own players and teams.
			      <br><br>Take to the field in this pick-up-and-play version of the national pastime. PlayStation gamers can create their own ballplayer characters and baseball teams, and even choose a logo.
			      <br><br>Controls are designed to be straightforward and forgiving, with younger gamers in mind. Six different stadiums and other customization options are intended to keep baseball fans of all ages coming back to try new variations of play.
			      <br><br>Features:
			      <br>Customize teams, logos, and player ratings
			      <br>Compete in a choice of six stadiums
			      <br>Challenge a friend or the computer
			      <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>Belt one outta the field!
                  <br>We took Sandlot Baseball to all-new levels of fun and excitement! Big League Slugger Baseball gives players the purest form of the game just like in those pick-up games in the sandlots across America! Big League Slugger Baseball No complex rules or impossible button combos to remember - it's just "Hey Batta-Batta! SWING!" for the love of the game!
                  <br><br>Take to the gridiron in this fantastic version of the national pastime. You can create your own players and teams, and even choose a logo. Other customization options are designed to keep you coming back to try new game play variation.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third person perspective.</li>
			<li>3D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Baseball theme.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

